Settings Features:
    • Custom Shortcuts: Create and manage personalized keyboard shortcuts.
    • Gamification: Utilize gamification elements to enhance user engagement such as: badges, chalanges, goals and rankings
    • manage users: manage and invit users to your company, control there exess rights and add them as emplyees.
    • Languges: setup your envirment with diferent languges and switch between them when desierd.
    • multi company: setup muiltible companyees within your organisation.
    • e-mail: Manage and setup incomming and uotgoing emails using aliases and automated prosesses.

